ctive of Cady, deciding that anyone that comes between them should be met with violence.</p><p> The character was a huge hit on TikTok, with users replicating a scene where M3GAN dances that became popular when it was shown as part of the film&#39;s trailer. In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/m3gan-review-horror-tiktok-3380522"><em>NME’s</em> four-star review for the film</a> , critic Nick Levin wrote that the film “has clearly been crafted with a future franchise in mind, but it&#39;s hard to be mad it when the character has such potential”.</p><p> After <em>M3GAN 2.0&#39;s</em> June release, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/m3gan-is-getting-an-erotic-thriller-spin-off-soulm8te-3767502">an erotic thriller spin-off, titled <em>SOULM8TE</em></a> , is scheduled for release in 2026. Last year, it was revealed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/you-can-now-buy-a-life-sized-replica-of-the-m3gan-doll-3613078">fans of the film could buy a life-size replica figure of M3GAN</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/m3gan-sequel-trailer-released-chappell-roan-3834056">M3GAN dances to Chappell Roan in new &#39;M3GAN 2.0&#39; trailer</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
